Ya tuhanku.

174
00:12:09,500 --> 00:12:12,041
Itu mesti
bagaimana semua ini bermula.

175
00:12:12,666 --> 00:12:13,500
Tunggu!

176
00:12:14,250 --> 00:12:15,250
Tengok.

177
00:12:20,625 --> 00:12:24,166
Benda itu, seperti, memukul tumbuhan
